Coutinho: &ldquo;The team were very focused right from the first minute. It&rsquo;s been a while since we picked up a good win.&rdquo;

Mourinho on critics of MUFC approach: 'I never speak about injuries. Other managers, they cry, they cry, they cry when a player is injured'<br />
<br />
Mourinho after the 0-0 at Anfield: &quot;I have no midfield to do what I usually do. No Fellaini, no Carrick, no Pogba - nothing, nothing at all&quot;

Klopp on Mane: &quot;Sadio is still in rehab. Indoors. Not even any exercises outside yet, If he's fit earlier (than 6 weeks) I'll be happy.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;I can imagine they (Senegal) feel the pressure a little bit. If Sadio is fit then we can't hide him. In this moment, I don't know.&quot;
